name: Special Edition Mix Tape Pouch - Love Mix Blue
description:
This bright and cheery zippered pouch is made in the likeness of a cassette tape. 

Made with Holland 100% wool felt. 100% wool felt is a high quality felt that is far more beautiful and durable than acrylic or wool blend felt. It doesn't get really fuzzy from use like acrylic felt and the colors are more rich and radiant. 

All of the applique features are hand cut and the larger pieces are attached by machine. The smaller and more intricate pieces are attached by hand or hand-embroidered on. The label, which reads "Love Mix" is also hand-embroidered. 

The construction of pouch is done by machine for strength and sturdiness. Fully lined with cotton fabric; lining will vary.


Dimensions 5.875"w x 3.75"h(approx. 14.92cm x 9.52cm)


You'll want to put this pouch in your boombox and crank the volume, but don't... It's perfect for storing your makeup, ipod, cellphone or keys and cash!

Handmade by Lindsey Porter
